local governments held here today that the National Union for the
Total Independence of Angola (UNITA) had pledged to cooperate
with the government to ensure the work go on smoothly.
</P>
<P>
According to the government official, the work of
re-establishing local governments will be completed by
mid-October with focus on Angolan border areas. 
