<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, August 19 (Xinhua) -- The Bank of China announced
today that Yang Zilin, vice-chairman of the Bank of China,
chief executive of the Bank of China Hong Kong-Macao Regional
Office and general manager of the Hong Kong Branch, will soon be
returning to the head office in Beijing.
</P>
<P>
Yang will assume the position of Executive Vice-President of
the Industrial and Commercial Bank of China.
</P>
<P>
