It said that the company now ranks first in China in terms of
quality, production and sales of pianos. Last year it produced
over 50,000 pianos, half of the country's total output.
</P>
<P>
The Firs Group, one of the country's leading clothing
manufacturers, can serve as another example of successful
marketing, according to the article.
</P>
<P>
Based in Ningbo, a port city in east China's Zhejiang Province,
the Firs Group owns over 20 marketing companies throughout China,
with a sales promotion contingent of more than 1,200 people. It
also opened over 500 special counters and collection stores in all
large and medium-sized cities across the country.
