<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, August 19 (Xinhua) -- South African President
Nelson Mandela will visit Switzerland early next month for the
anouncement of the successful bidder for the 2004 Olympic Games,
local daily the Citizen reported today.
</P>
