information on the flight safety, as well as to organize more
meetings between relevant experts.
</P>
<P>
According to Higgins, both sides also discussed the use by
american air companies of the Russian air space, and both have
reached an understanding on the creation of a joint group of
experts to prepare feasibility studies for the opening of new
trans-polar routes, for example, from the United States to the
South-East Asia which are expected to go over the territory of
Russia.
</P>
<P>
It said the United States will finance Boeing experts on the
score, while Russia will finance FAS experts. 
